string_data: The image shows a woman in dark clothing speaking into a microphone at what appears to be a protest or demonstration. Behind her, supporters are dressed in period costume resembling suffragettes, wearing sashes and holding various signs including "WOMEN DEMAND CLIMATE JUSTICE" and "CONSCIENTIOUS PROTECTION FOR CHILDREN OF ALL LIFE." A large red banner with partial text is visible in the background, along with rainbow-colored flags. The scene takes place outdoors with bare trees visible.
